1BB7  9C 06               1488  ?AG27	LEAI	2+?AG3,S		Point to buffer
1BB9  AA                  1489  	STB	I		Save it
1BBA  08 01               1490  	LDB	#1		Get 1
1BBC  AC 03               1491  	STB	2+?AG5,S
